{"name":"Greed (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has an excessive desire to acquire or possess material wealth.</p>\n<p>The character will go to great lengths to obtain wealth, but would not betray trusted friends, steal or commit unconscionable acts to do so.</p>","flawName":"Greed","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"0q9ImEljmNlQoaaE"}
{"name":"Obese (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is obese, suffering the consequences of a deteriorating physique.</p>\n<p>Movement rate is reduced by 1. In addition to reduced movement the character suffers -1 to all physical actions due to his or her immense weight and ungainliness. Clothes and armour must be custom made.</p>","flawName":"Obese","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Stamina"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.p6LxL723IOKdlLXS"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"1s5YNdXS4SY2YQyt"}
{"name":"Amnesia (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character suffers from memory loss and has difficulties remembering the past.</p>\n<p>The character has severe amnesia and has forgotten portions of their past. The amnesia may be natural, or trauma-induced. In addition to the effects of mild amnesia, the character has forgotten noteworthy events from their past, such as making a powerful enemy, which may come back to haunt them.</p>","flawName":"Amnesia","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Intellect"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ryIeI09MfRBKrpkv"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"2v3xe0wUPlszuRA3"}
{"name":"Bleeder (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character bruises easily and his or her blood does not clot normally, making even scratches perilous due to uncontrolled bleeding.</p>\n<p>Natural healing is reduced by one, meaning for instance that it takes a character with a Stamina score of one (1) two full days to heal one point of Health.</p>","flawName":"Bleeder","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Stamina"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"6bg0p6XZFlg18iPL"}
{"name":"Social Stigma (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character belongs to a faction, species or occupation, which is considered inferior or abhorrent to the general population of Llyhn. He or she is easily recognisable as belonging to this group and meets bias accordingly. Harlots, certain religious groups, slaves and the like are examples of stigmatised groups.</p>\n<p>The character belongs to a grouping generally met with distrust. The character must provide proof of their words (or actions) to gain any credibility. Their motives are always questioned. Severe: Many people actively avoid the character. They are loathed, and few would care to be caught anywhere near them.</p>","flawName":"Social Stigma","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Presence"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pwnxlIos8y9SyM7j"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"7qT1mlBelNXMSe5z"}
{"name":"Addiction (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is addicted to a substance and requires frequent satiation. They must feed their addiction daily and are likely to go to great lengths to obtain whatever it is they crave. If the character is unable to get the substance, they experience withdrawal and become erratic or bad-tempered; suffering a -1 penalty to all actions per severity tier of the Flaw.</p>\n<p>The character is addicted to a substance that is either incapacitating / hallucinogenic or which is very expensive or dangerous to obtain.</p>","flawName":"Addiction","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"8B3Bl3MdPshanex5"}
{"name":"Easily Exhausted (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character&rsquo;s muscles tire and acidify quickly, leaving him or her are unable to maintain feats of strength for very long. Actions included are climbing, carrying heavy loads, fighting and any other tiring activities as determined by the Arbiter. The Strength score and flaw severity determine how long the character can function at normal capacity. After that, the character suffers a -1 penalty to all physical actions for each period exceeding the time limit.</p>\n<p>The character can perform intense work for up to 6 seconds (2 combat rounds) without penalty.</p>","flawName":"Easily Exhausted","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Strength"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"9UeeOUOcYz7fpJI2"}
{"name":"Bad Aura (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has an appearance that instils distrust and suspicion. Whenever he or she meets new people, there is a chance that they are instinctively biased against the character. Whether the bias is based on fact is more or less irrelevant, what counts is what people believe to be true.</p>\n<p>Based on gut instinct, people assume the character is a murderer or other delinquent, likely faulting him or her for random crimes or deeds and treating him or her with acute prejudice. A -3 penalty is applied to all response rolls.</p>","flawName":"Bad Aura","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Presence"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"CythYchBHFiX3HqE"}
{"name":"Frail","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is very frail and has difficulties carrying and wielding heavy objects. Count the strength score as one less than it is when calculating item or weapon size modifiers as well as armour bulk. All actions involving lifting and carrying take a -1 penalty.</p>","flawName":"Frail","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Stamina"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.p6LxL723IOKdlLXS"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"D4YDcYub5664LjWd"}
{"name":"Impulsive","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character habitually follows his or her immediate urges and, in most cases, act first and think later. Being impulsive is not the same as being stupid or suicidal, but the inclination to consider options or plan before taking action is usually absent.</p>","flawName":"Impulsive","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"F0MXPzxAtbPcfzDK"}
{"name":"Primitive (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character either comes from a primitive background or has difficulties fathoming complexities beyond the basic needs of survival and procreation.</p>\n<p>The character can function in society but must pay an extra point cost to acquire mental and social oriented skills.</p>","flawName":"Primitive","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Intellect"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PbLHGPIV6I00Cx91"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"FKZSwKOx5WFU6gxy"}
{"name":"Blunt (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is incredibly blunt and opinionated about thoughts, feelings and viewpoints. They see no reason to be diplomatic about anything and have no qualms about expressing their views, even when it may be unwise to do so.</p>\n<p>The character&rsquo;s candour is brusque. Although neither stupid nor suicidal, their loutish manners and inability to restrain behaviour will cause problems. The character suffers a -3 to reaction rolls and a -3 penalty to social rolls and must make a Willpower roll [7] to lie or act with restraint.</p>","flawName":"Blunt","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Persuasion"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"FQ1AUogFbUUGoUsI"}
{"name":"Emaciated (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is unusually skinny and malnourished compared to the norm. He or she has very little body fat and muscle, making her tire easily and succumbing to fatigue. An emaciated character cannot maintain arduous physical activity for very long without the risk of succumbing to exhaustion. Continued strenuous activity, such as athletics or fighting, requires a successful Stamina roll of [7] every (Stamina score times 6) seconds. Failure means the character collapses with exhaustion and must rest for an equal amount of time.</p>\n<p>The flaw severity depends on the character&rsquo;s Stamina score.</p>","flawName":"Emaciated","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Stamina"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.b2hDFCppj0F3jomE"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"G2aog2wVbH2CLwZB"}
{"name":"Repulsive Habits (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>This character behaves in a manner that is repulsive. Depending on the severity of the Flaw the habit is increasingly disgusting or appalling. The player must specify the offensive habit.</p>\n<p>The character has constant mannerisms or habits which aggravate people, causing a -2 penalty to all social interaction.</p>","flawName":"Repulsive Habits","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Presence"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pwnxlIos8y9SyM7j"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"I8dgmeULR3O2S6nP"}
{"name":"Easily Exhausted (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character&rsquo;s muscles tire and acidify quickly, leaving him or her are unable to maintain feats of strength for very long. Actions included are climbing, carrying heavy loads, fighting and any other tiring activities as determined by the Arbiter. The Strength score and flaw severity determine how long the character can function at normal capacity. After that, the character suffers a -1 penalty to all physical actions for each period exceeding the time limit.</p>\n<p>The character can sustain heavy labour for 30 seconds (10 combat rounds).</p>","flawName":"Easily Exhausted","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Strength"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"JMQAaKoZSO2IAC3a"}
{"name":"Distracted","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has a short attention span and finds it hard to focus on tasks taking more than a few minutes. When engaged in prolonged tasks or performing extended actions apply a -1 penalty for every additional roll required.</p>","flawName":"Distracted","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Intellect"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PbLHGPIV6I00Cx91"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"KUFRbzMpWDq01IDf"}
{"name":"Lack of Situational Awareness (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is lacking when it comes to reading body language and noticing social indicators in interaction, appropriateness or manners. Apply a -1 penalty to all social actions such as diplomacy, negotiating and socialising. The character may seem eccentric, rude or uncaring to others.</p>","flawName":"Lack of Situational Awareness","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Awareness"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"Kq8H4aZpoRPVwsXw"}
{"name":"Low Pain Tolerance (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is very sensitive to pain and reacts strongly to even minor injuries and the threat of bodily harm.</p>\n<p>The character tries to avoid getting hurt at all costs and if injured he or she must pass a Fear roll [4] or roll fear effect 1-4.</p>","flawName":"Low Pain Tolerance","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Stamina"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.p6LxL723IOKdlLXS"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"LBDwZuVYPKMg5MVs"}
{"name":"Outspoken (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is incapable of cunning and guile.</p>\n<p>The character cannot lie or apply exploitation intentionally. They may be able to omit the truth but are unable to lie directly.</p>","flawName":"Outspoken","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Persuasion"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.mdW6e9O4aDSOp7Qx"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"LicCtgIOJl2QfkAp"}
{"name":"Lack of Situational Awareness (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is devoid of situational awareness; completely lacking the ability to understand, assess and interpret reactional patterns; he or she has no grasp of what is proper and act exclusively on personal wants and needs. The character has a hard time functioning within any society as this behaviour tends to provoke most people. The character may not acquire any skills with social uses and suffers a -3 penalty to social actions.</p>","flawName":"Lack of Situational Awareness","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Awareness"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"LiwXuagXTHG0B5ls"}
{"name":"Sluggish (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has an unwieldy body, which will not (re)act in a fast manner. No matter how hard he or she tries, actions are always sluggish and slow.</p>\n<p>Suffer a -1 penalty to move, initiative and surprise rolls.</p>","flawName":"Sluggish","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Agility"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"MJA778wOXvLCINiX"}
{"name":"Obvious Body Language (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>This character&rsquo;s body language reveals his or her thoughts and intentions. Although the character may have no reservations about lying, he or she is rarely successful because the facial expression or body-language gives the real purpose away immediately.</p>\n<p>The character suffers a -1 penalty to attempts at subterfuge, deception and exploitation.</p>","flawName":"Obvious Body Language","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Persuasion"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.mdW6e9O4aDSOp7Qx"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"N6d74zIeweLLyqM3"}
{"name":"Social Stigma (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character belongs to a faction, species or occupation, which is considered inferior or abhorrent to the general population of Llyhn. He or she is easily recognisable as belonging to this group and meets bias accordingly. Harlots, certain religious groups, slaves and the like are examples of stigmatised groups.</p>\n<p>Many people actively avoid the character. They are loathed, and few would care to be caught anywhere near them.</p>","flawName":"Social Stigma","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Presence"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pwnxlIos8y9SyM7j"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"NC38yaBX8awHr2Bw"}
{"name":"Lameness (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>For whatever reason, the character suffers from lameness in the legs or lower torso impeding or preventing movement and general mobility.</p>\n<p>The legs are paralysed, and the character is unable to walk on your own. Do not select this flaw if the character has an attribute or Talent rendering the Flaw immaterial - such as flying.</p>","flawName":"Lameness","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Agility"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"NPENn8u49PMbQOVS"}
{"name":"Bad Temper (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character suffers from a notoriously bad temper and has a tough time controlling his or her reactions. He or she reacts strongly to any slight, imagined or real.</p>\n<p>When exposed to provocation or a stressful situation they tend to respond aggressively, with an angry retort, insults or shouting, unless they succeed in a Willpower roll (Arbiter&rsquo;s discretion as to difficulty). Although reactions are rarely violent without an actual threat, situations can escalate quickly.</p>","flawName":"Bad Temper","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"NrCzyVs1I6NEv0b4"}
{"name":"Clueless","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character lacks social awareness and rarely understands or grasps the meaning in subtle interactions with other people. They know what people say, but often miss implied meaning or nuance in conversations. In situations where information is hinted at or passed discretely, the character must make an Intellect roll to see the message is understood (Arbiter decides difficulty). Situations such as flirting, irony, gestures and other non-obvious communication attempts require a roll.</p>","flawName":"Clueless","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Intellect"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PbLHGPIV6I00Cx91"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"OSZBXZekdCAEQ3Wk"}
{"name":"Bad Aura (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has an appearance that instils distrust and suspicion. Whenever he or she meets new people, there is a chance that they are instinctively biased against the character. Whether the bias is based on fact is more or less irrelevant, what counts is what people believe to be true.</p>\n<p>The character is assumed to be a crook, thief or charlatan and so on, making people apprehensive in their company; for instance refusing to serve the character and causing a -2 response penalty.</p>","flawName":"Bad Aura","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Presence"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"OTJnXXdng8TQhpjr"}
{"name":"Primitive (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character either comes from a primitive background or has difficulties fathoming complexities beyond the basic needs of survival and procreation.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The character struggles to interact in civilised society, suffers -1 to all social rolls and must pay double point cost for all mental and social skills.</p>","flawName":"Primitive","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Intellect"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PbLHGPIV6I00Cx91"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"OW1bdqKszyyshm5T"}
{"name":"Bad Temper (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character suffers from a notoriously bad temper and has a tough time controlling his or her reactions. He or she reacts strongly to any slight, imagined or real.</p>\n<p>When exposed to provocation or a stressful situation they tend to respond aggressively, with an angry retort, insults or shouting, unless they succeed in a Willpower roll (Arbiter&rsquo;s discretion as to difficulty). The character threatens violence if provoked.</p>","flawName":"Bad Temper","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"P0SZPWCg5V5aTGT6"}
{"name":"Weak Grip (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>Weak hands mean this character easily drops held items. This typically affects acrobatics, climbing, fighting and other actions involving held items and requiring a firm grip.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>A natural roll of 1-2 causes the character to lose their grip.</p>","flawName":"Weak Grip","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Strength"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"P9ezII0RT6XIXeCZ"}
{"name":"Hideous (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is ugly and is &ndash; as a consequence - often treated unfairly or poorly compared to others. Hideous characters suffer a -1 penalty to all initial response modifiers.</p>","flawName":"Hideous","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Presence"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pwnxlIos8y9SyM7j"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"Q9fwKEIm2ballhX7"}
{"name":"Impaired Vision (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has impaired vision which affects his or her ability to act and perform actions based on sight.</p>\n<p>The character&rsquo;s vision is blurry causing him or her problems seeing faraway objects clearly and judging distances. Apply a penalty of -1 when using missile or thrown weapons, when dealing with spatial actions such as judging distance and all spotting rolls.</p>","flawName":"Impaired Vision","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Awareness"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"Rbz2wiRkxKHLXUbE"}
{"name":"Addiction (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is addicted to a substance and requires frequent satiation. They must feed their addiction daily and are likely to go to great lengths to obtain whatever it is they crave. If the character is unable to get the substance, they experience withdrawal and become erratic or bad-tempered; suffering a -1 penalty to all actions per severity tier of the Flaw.</p>\n<p>The addiction is to a substance that is intoxicating but allows the character to retain some control of herself while under the influence.</p>","flawName":"Addiction","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"SHPWatucxwbsl08h"}
{"name":"Cramps (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character&rsquo;s muscles tend to cramp up at inopportune moments during physical activity. Only the muscles involved in the action get cramps - if the character is arm-wrestling just the arm and hand will cramp up, so they may still get up and walk away.</p>\n<p>A critical failure or a natural roll of 1 while performing a physical action triggers cramps, temporarily preventing activity. If the action involves using an item (such as a weapon) the character will drop it. The pains will subside within D12 minutes.</p>","flawName":"Cramps","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Strength"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"SgqBKGQHOXI2eQp7"}
{"name":"Blunt (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is incredibly blunt and opinionated about thoughts, feelings and viewpoints. They see no reason to be diplomatic about anything and have no qualms about expressing their views, even when it may be unwise to do so.</p>\n<p>The character feels a need to voice opinions regularly and has no qualms divulging their views no matter how inappropriate or untimely it may be. The character suffers a -1 to reaction rolls and a -3 penalty to social rolls.</p>","flawName":"Blunt","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Persuasion"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"T10F4vO3ShnVQ003"}
{"name":"Clumsy (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is unusually clumsy and tends to blunder into things causing commotion and annoyance. The clumsiness is very rarely life- threatening, but it is annoying and sometimes costly.</p>\n<p>All Agility-based rolls of a natural 1-3 counts as a critical failure and during combat a +1 modifier is added to rolls on the critical mishap table.</p>","flawName":"Clumsy","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Agility"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"T1rl5pLIONFvH8dU"}
{"name":"Sluggish (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has an unwieldy body, which will not (re)act in a fast manner. No matter how hard he or she tries, actions are always sluggish and slow.</p>\n<p>The character has a -2 penalty to move, initiative and surprise rolls, and can only use reaction manoeuvres as delayed actions, never as reactions.</p>","flawName":"Sluggish","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Agility"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"U78IckmEAfZUPJx3"}
{"name":"Outspoken (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is incapable of cunning and guile.</p>\n<p>Not only can the character not lie or omit pertinent facts, but they also cannot use or condone deceitful methods.</p>","flawName":"Outspoken","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Persuasion"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.mdW6e9O4aDSOp7Qx"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"V9MqBZk1RMPzcyrH"}
{"name":"Bad Temper (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character suffers from a notoriously bad temper and has a tough time controlling his or her reactions. He or she reacts strongly to any slight, imagined or real. Mild:</p>\n<p>When exposed to provocation or a stressful situation they tend to respond aggressively, with an angry retort, insults or shouting, unless they succeed in a Willpower roll (Arbiter&rsquo;s discretion as to difficulty). The character responds violently to provocation.</p>","flawName":"Bad Temper","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"VsIrReF3PWvbtRWk"}
{"name":"Bleeder (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character bruises easily and his or her blood does not clot normally, making even scratches perilous due to uncontrolled bleeding.</p>\n<p>Natural healing is reduced by one, meaning for instance that it takes a character with a Stamina score of one (1) two full days to heal one point of Health. In addition to reduced healing rate the character bleeds excessively once wounded, suffering a loss of one point of Health per combat round until bandaged. Further to reduced healing rate any injury counts as minor bleeding wounds for the character.</p>","flawName":"Bleeder","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Stamina"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"XU6TjtUJRJnLg5IA"}
{"name":"Lameness (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>For whatever reason, the character suffers from lameness in the legs or lower torso impeding or preventing movement and general mobility.</p>\n<p>The character has significantly impaired mobility and walks awkwardly; this causes halved movement rate, and the character is unable to sprint.</p>","flawName":"Lameness","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Agility"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"XYM97OVbiH5g0csU"}
{"name":"Addiction (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is addicted to a substance and requires frequent satiation. They must feed their addiction daily and are likely to go to great lengths to obtain whatever it is they crave. If the character is unable to get the substance, they experience withdrawal and become erratic or bad-tempered; suffering a -1 penalty to all actions per severity tier of the Flaw.</p>\n<p>The addiction is focused on smoking herbs, exclusively drinking tea or some other relatively inconsequential addiction that the character, however, must uphold. This is a minor but continuous expense and bother.</p>","flawName":"Addiction","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"XkkyHL5HdCPG03Ql"}
{"name":"No Orientation Sense","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has no sense of direction or navigational skills and gets lost even in familiar places. How anybody can follow a map is an enigma resulting in the character suffering a -3 penalty to all skills involving orienteering or navigation and wilderness survival.</p>","flawName":"No Orientation Sense","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Awareness"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"XnwlhvE0pecnwlrs"}
{"name":"Clumsy (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is unusually clumsy and tends to blunder into things causing commotion and annoyance. The clumsiness is very rarely life- threatening, but it is annoying and sometimes costly.</p>\n<p>Any Agility-based action suffers a critical failure on a roll of 1-2, causing minor accidents or mishaps.</p>","flawName":"Clumsy","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Agility"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"dBxt2lVYGtv99b49"}
{"name":"Obese (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is obese, suffering the consequences of a deteriorating physique.</p>\n<p>Movement rate is reduced by 3. In addition to reduced movement the character suffers -3 to all physical actions due to his or her immense weight and ungainliness. Clothes and armour must be custom made.</p>","flawName":"Obese","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Stamina"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.p6LxL723IOKdlLXS"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"eB6AZd2vceLBAVUM"}
{"name":"Eunuch","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>Whether voluntarily, in an accident or through a hostile deed the character was castrated in early puberty. He retains a boyish appearance and often a high- pitched voice. Eunuchs may be met with contempt or ridicule, and are often sought after by slavers. Only male characters can have this Flaw.</p>","flawName":"Eunuch","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Presence"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pwnxlIos8y9SyM7j"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"eDMVK8pwgiHSe2rW"}
{"name":"Butter-Fingered","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>Such tiny things! The character has trouble manipulating small objects and threading a needle is an almost impossible feat. Actions involving fine motor skills have a high probability of going awry. To illustrate this, add a -1 penalty to all actions involving small objects, craft-skills and any actions the Arbiter deem appropriate.</p>","flawName":"Butter-Fingered","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Agility"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.eAv54p3xXwo7lpUQ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"fZgJdkqLNdLUy4ou"}
{"name":"Indecisive (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has difficulties making up his or her mind and continually changes their opinion. This is evident whenever he or she is faced with a decision or providing a point in a conversation.</p>\n<p>The character never seems able to decide upon any given course of action or opinion. Only if pressured or forced by circumstances will the character choose a course of action.</p>","flawName":"Indecisive","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"gnTGUvRI1Hb8VLIb"}
{"name":"Impaired Vision (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has impaired vision which affects his or her ability to act and perform actions based on sight.</p>\n<p>The characters eyes are very sensitive to light with daylight being practically blinding, causing -3 to all actions using sight. If the character can shade his or her eyes during daylight hours, the penalty is -1. Low to moderate lighting, such as during dusk and dawn confers no penalty. The character suffers the usual penalties for dark conditions. Do not select this flaw if the character has an attribute or Talent rendering the Flaw immaterial.</p>","flawName":"Impaired Vision","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Awareness"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"hjzpEkrOoQAyWOnm"}
{"name":"No Empathy (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>This character has little understanding of feelings in general, and practically no appreciation for the emotions of others. He or she may have no difficulty relating to his or her own emotional state but is rarely concerned with how actions affect others as their feelings and thoughts or beliefs have little or no significance.</p>\n<p>The emotions of others are a complete mystery, and the character suffers -1 penalty to all social interaction and a -3 penalty to all actions directly involving the appreciation and awareness of emotional motivation, including deciphering sentient behaviour.</p>","flawName":"No Empathy","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Awareness"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"hkK8Xoa6L5ZZtCmJ"}
{"name":"Obvious Body Language (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>This character&rsquo;s body-language reveals his or her thoughts and intentions. Although the character may have no reservations about lying, he or she is rarely successful because the facial expression or body-language gives the real purpose away immediately.</p>\n<p>Not only is any deception easily noticeable, but the body language is also so evident that opponents in combat can readily predict the intention and next action of the character; giving them a +1 to any reaction manoeuvre.</p>","flawName":"Obvious Body Language","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Persuasion"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.mdW6e9O4aDSOp7Qx"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"hnyvWcIlPbwNwpYc"}
{"name":"Confused","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character easily gets confused and has difficulties dealing with new impressions and situations; taking a long time to process information. In calm, familiar situations this Flaw is negligible, but stress or unfamiliarity almost certainly confuse the character. The character suffers a -1 penalty to all surprise rolls, and during hectic encounters and commotion, a successful Intellect roll is required for the character to react suitably to the situation (Arbiter determines difficulty) &mdash; the character is disoriented and unable to act on a failed roll. This flaw does not apply if the character is actively engaged in combat with an opponent, but applies as soon as the character is disengaged or unable to perceive his or her opponent.</p>","flawName":"Confused","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Intellect"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PbLHGPIV6I00Cx91"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"jX2zbt9UIBolwCyG"}
{"name":"Oblivious (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>Letters, numbers and abstract images do not make sense to the character.</p>\n<p>Any type of writing - pictographic, alphabetical or numerical - is beyond the character&rsquo;s abilities. They may never acquire the Reading-Writing Skill and are unable to comprehend any written message, abstract images or drawn representations.</p>","flawName":"Oblivious","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Intellect"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PbLHGPIV6I00Cx91"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"jixU4RcI6hd5Szxf"}
{"name":"Emaciated (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is unusually skinny and malnourished compared to the norm. He or she has very little body fat and muscle, making her tire easily and succumbing to fatigue. An emaciated character cannot maintain arduous physical activity for very long without the risk of succumbing to exhaustion. Continued strenuous activity, such as athletics or fighting, requires a successful Stamina roll of [7] every (Stamina score times 6) seconds. Failure means the character collapses with exhaustion and must rest for an equal amount of time.</p>\n<p>The flaw severity depends on the character&rsquo;s Stamina score.</p>","flawName":"Emaciated","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Stamina"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.p6LxL723IOKdlLXS"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"kWUo9F1Y0yhWZVI0"}
{"name":"Fanatic","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is zealous about a cause or an idea, following its creed with fanatical devotion. The devotion can be of any type or sort as long as the Arbiter approves but must require certain conduct or obedience to specific leaders or principles, significantly influencing the life of the character, to be acceptable. Although his or her every thought might not be bent upon the cause the character would never willingly betray the cause and count as having a Willpower score of 6 for actions involving defending their ideals.</p>","flawName":"Fanatic","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"kXielc7OCRzzft0Z"}
{"name":"Distinctive Appearance","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has a distinctive appearance, such as albinism, short stature or great height. They are easily noticeable and stand out in a crowd of peers, making people take note of and remember the character. As a result, they have a -1 on Subterfuge rolls. During violent encounters, some opponents may even be inclined to target the character if given a choice.</p>","flawName":"Distinctive Appearance","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Presence"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pwnxlIos8y9SyM7j"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"knXzSkGxRa1Ax2oF"}
{"name":"Low Pain Tolerance (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is very sensitive to pain and reacts strongly to even minor injuries and the threat of bodily harm.</p>\n<p>The character seeks to avoid encounters or activities which may result in physical harm. &ldquo;Bruised&rdquo; characters suffer a -1 penalty, while &ldquo;hurt&rdquo; and &ldquo;injured&rdquo; penalties are increased by a factor of one (1) and if injured the character must pass a Fear roll [4] or suffer fear effect 1-4.</p>","flawName":"Low Pain Tolerance","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Stamina"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.p6LxL723IOKdlLXS"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"l8gKoeMiu4NrPaCA"}
{"name":"Outspoken (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is incapable of cunning and guile.</p>\n<p>The character is outspoken to the point that they must proclaim the truth and the whole truth, no matter what. If they witness falsehood, exaggerated or restrained assertion of fact, they are compelled to clarify and call attention to the truth.</p>","flawName":"Outspoken","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Persuasion"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.mdW6e9O4aDSOp7Qx"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"l9v5HCW0f2mcdFky"}
{"name":"No Empathy (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>This character has little understanding of feelings in general, and practically no appreciation for the emotions of others. He or she may have no difficulty relating to his or her own emotional state but is rarely concerned with how actions affect others as their feelings and thoughts or beliefs have little or no significance.</p>\n<p>The character suffers a -1 penalty to all actions involving the comprehension or appreciation of emotions in others, making it hard to determine and analysing the motivation, wants and needs of others. Actions include carousing, flirting, bargaining, intrigue, socialising and subterfuge.</p>","flawName":"No Empathy","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Awareness"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"leytWNBPfrK7Foo1"}
{"name":"Low Pain Tolerance (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is very sensitive to pain and reacts strongly to even minor injuries and the threat of bodily harm.</p>\n<p>Same as above, but in encounters where physical harm is likely the character is affected by &ldquo;Fear&rdquo; [4] regardless of whether the threat becomes real or not.</p>","flawName":"Low Pain Tolerance","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Stamina"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.p6LxL723IOKdlLXS"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"mGNuT8juyBWRju9j"}
{"name":"Cramps (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character&rsquo;s muscles tend to cramp up at inopportune moments during physical activity. Only the muscles involved in the action get cramps - if the character is arm-wrestling just the arm and hand will cramp up, so they may still get up and walk away.</p>\n<p>A critically failed physical action causes cramps, leaving the character unable to continue using the cramped limb for D3 rounds.</p>","flawName":"Cramps","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Strength"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"mICkZPncGqYkKn4M"}
{"name":"Emaciated (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is unusually skinny and malnourished compared to the norm. He or she has very little body fat and muscle, making her tire easily and succumbing to fatigue. An emaciated character cannot maintain arduous physical activity for very long without the risk of succumbing to exhaustion. Continued strenuous activity, such as athletics or fighting, requires a successful Stamina roll of [7] every (Stamina score times 6) seconds. Failure means the character collapses with exhaustion and must rest for an equal amount of time.</p>\n<p>The flaw severity depends on the character&rsquo;s Stamina score.</p>","flawName":"Emaciated","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Stamina"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.65QZOEIZ9aLZyBiA"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"nk4Ra7eWxWy93cWe"}
{"name":"Greed (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has an excessive desire to acquire or possess material wealth.</p>\n<p>The character is generally not above cheating and lying to obtain the wealth that should &ldquo;rightfully&rdquo; be his or hers. The character might even consider being disloyal to the people close to him or her if the promise of riches is great enough.</p>","flawName":"Greed","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"nvmCOOOoedeMd4Ek"}
{"name":"Impaired Vision (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has impaired vision which affects his or her ability to act and perform actions based on sight.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The character is partially blind requiring extensive effort to see beyond his or her own hands. All actions requiring sight are at -1 penalty and using a thrown or missile weapon is possible only at short range and with the -1 penalty. Judging distances and spotting rolls are at -3 penalty.</p>","flawName":"Impaired Vision","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Awareness"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"oAq6RTO70FZEWmbn"}
{"name":"Oblivious (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>Letters, numbers and abstract images do not make sense to the character.</p>\n<p>The character can understand (but not replicate) pictographic forms of writing. They find it hard, but not impossible, to grasp written numbers. Alphabetical reading or writing is beyond their abilities, and they may not acquire the Reading-Writing Skill.</p>","flawName":"Oblivious","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Intellect"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PbLHGPIV6I00Cx91"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"oDU6SowcseKTkizu"}
{"name":"Indecisive (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has difficulties making up his or her mind and continually changes their opinion. This is evident whenever he or she is faced with a decision or providing a point in a conversation.</p>\n<p>When trying to decide the character display doubt about all alternative opinions and only come to a conclusion after having reviewed and weighed all options methodically.</p>","flawName":"Indecisive","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"oTjNkx6Y237sM5U6"}
{"name":"Repulsive Habits (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>This character behaves in a manner that is repulsive. Depending on the severity of the Flaw the habit is increasingly disgusting or appalling. The player must specify the offensive habit.</p>\n<p>The habit is more annoying than repulsive but serves to irritate the people, sparking dislike. Apply a -1 penalty to social interaction. Habits may include excessive boasting, lack of personal hygiene, being judgemental, and so on.</p>","flawName":"Repulsive Habits","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Presence"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pwnxlIos8y9SyM7j"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"ocFTOiqJIRYMnPSU"}
{"name":"Cramps (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character&rsquo;s muscles tend to cramp up at inopportune moments during physical activity. Only the muscles involved in the action get cramps - if the character is arm-wrestling just the arm and hand will cramp up, so they may still get up and walk away.</p>\n<p>A critical failure or a natural roll of 1 while performing a physical action triggers cramps, temporarily preventing activity. If the action involves using an item (such as a weapon) the character will drop it. The pains will subside within 3D12 seconds or D12 combat rounds.</p>","flawName":"Cramps","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Strength"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"p86N3yAEG26hVwAF"}
{"name":"Exotic Illness","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character suffers from a strange, incurable disease. Although not fatal it makes life miserable; the character tires quickly, and has coughing fits and nausea. Once a day make a Stamina roll [7] or suffer -1 to all physically based actions that day. If the Arbiter allows, drugs, herbs or other curatives ease the symptoms of the disease for that day. These are either very costly or difficult to obtain.</p>","flawName":"Exotic Illness","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Stamina"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.b2hDFCppj0F3jomE"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"qFHH7pWGf5ru8CFh"}
{"name":"Bleeder (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character bruises easily and his or her blood does not clot normally, making even scratches perilous due to uncontrolled bleeding.</p>\n<p>Natural healing is reduced by one, meaning for instance that it takes a character with a Stamina score of one (1) two full days to heal one point of Health. In addition to reduced healing rate the character bleeds excessively once wounded, suffering a loss of one point of Health per combat round until bandaged.</p>","flawName":"Bleeder","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Stamina"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.sxdHspNyFfPYd8Ht"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"qcCjHgCU5QlYvZ7t"}
{"name":"Night Blindness","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has severely impaired vision in low light conditions. Double all penalties for poor lighting (to a maximum of -12) when performing actions which require the use of eyesight.</p>","flawName":"Night Blindness","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Awareness"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"quPYuMGhJcbzt5SF"}
{"name":"Gullibility","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is na&iuml;ve, easily manipulated and believes most anything they are told. They have difficulties reading people&rsquo;s intentions or underlying motives. The character suffers a -1 penalty to resist persuasion, influence and domination.</p>","flawName":"Gullibility","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Intellect"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PbLHGPIV6I00Cx91"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"sL8yhoZ0yAsZGUmR"}
{"name":"Weak Will (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has little resolve and submits under even slight pressure. He or she is easily frightened and bullied and suffers a -1 penalty when resisting temptation, persuasion, intimidation, fear, awe or coercion. The character may know that what he or she is doing is wrong or not in their best self-interest but lacks the backbone to do otherwise.</p>","flawName":"Weak Will","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"sM6nxxc0iHiDRCqh"}
{"name":"Obese (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is obese, suffering the consequences of a deteriorating physique.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Movement rate is reduced by 1.</p>","flawName":"Obese","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Stamina"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.p6LxL723IOKdlLXS"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"sgKxfKI2Z70su9hQ"}
{"name":"Compulsive Liar (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>Reality and truth have little relevance to the character, and consequently they understate, embellish or lie constantly, not out of ill will but because they cannot control it.</p>\n<p>The character thrives on telling tall tales and embellishing the truth to the extreme, but most of the stories have a basis in reality.</p>","flawName":"Compulsive Liar","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"ta4U7aG3kKeNqNWs"}
{"name":"Savant","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is an idiot savant, with severe mental challenges, but displaying remarkable ability within a few specified fields of knowledge. The character is only allowed to acquire 6 skills, including combat skills, and suffers a -1 penalty to all social actions.</p>","flawName":"Savant","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Intellect"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PbLHGPIV6I00Cx91"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"thRiCKYamF5iBDVg"}
{"name":"Weak Grip (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>Weak hands mean this character easily drops held items. This typically affects acrobatics, climbing, fighting and other actions involving held items and requiring a firm grip.</p>\n<p>The character loses their grip on a natural roll of 1-3.</p>","flawName":"Weak Grip","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Strength"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"twAOkfoT7PQi4sHQ"}
{"name":"Blunt (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is incredibly blunt and opinionated about thoughts, feelings and viewpoints. They see no reason to be diplomatic about anything and have no qualms about expressing their views, even when it may be unwise to do so.</p>\n<p>The character speaks their mind although he or she may attempt to do so in somewhat subtle ways or with tact. Apply a -1 penalty to social actions.</p>","flawName":"Blunt","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Persuasion"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"uLbhBOe8EABPMxwR"}
{"name":"Weak Grip (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>Weak hands mean this character easily drops held items. This typically affects acrobatics, climbing, fighting and other actions involving held items and requiring a firm grip.</p>\n<p>On a natural roll of 1 a held item is dropped in addition to any other mishap.</p>","flawName":"Weak Grip","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Strength"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"uN82VhmoLS6W2Pfr"}
{"name":"Bad Aura (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character has an appearance that instils distrust and suspicion. Whenever he or she meets new people, there is a chance that they are instinctively biased against the character. Whether the bias is based on fact is more or less irrelevant, what counts is what people believe to be true.</p>\n<p>People instantly suppose the character to be a scoundrel or otherwise mildly suspicious causing a -1 response penalty until trust is established.</p>","flawName":"Bad Aura","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Presence"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"vHvDNxvBBTH4vnAQ"}
{"name":"Compulsive Liar (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>Reality and truth have little relevance to the character, and consequently they understate, embellish or lie constantly, not out of ill will but because they cannot control it.</p>\n<p>The character does not care about truth and has no qualms about fabricating incidences, references or complete anecdotes. They say anything they please, for whatever reason, to whomever they want. If the character is intent on conveying the exact truth, a successful Willpower roll is required to do so.</p>","flawName":"Compulsive Liar","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Willpower"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SaY742Las21LUIVZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"vWzBy7tSSIuOdqJT"}
{"name":"Hideous (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character is profoundly scarred, disfigured or otherwise repugnant. Some people may even experience revulsion on seeing them and although this may work as an advantage when trying to intimidate or frighten people, it hampers the character in most social situations, applying a -2 penalty to all social interaction, including initial response rolls.</p>","flawName":"Hideous","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Presence"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pwnxlIos8y9SyM7j"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"wSnZ4zDCdogqHznF"}
{"name":"Repulsive Habits (Severe)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>This character behaves in a manner that is repulsive. Depending on the severity of the Flaw the habit is increasingly disgusting or appalling. The player must specify the offensive habit.</p>\n<p>You have habits which will revolt even the most stalwart of people, causing a -3 penalty to all social interaction. Habits may include cannibalism, collecting and wearing cadaverous remains and so on.</p>","flawName":"Repulsive Habits","severity":"Severe","associatedAbility":"Presence"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pwnxlIos8y9SyM7j"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"xDuf6tYXfZVIvFZ9"}
{"name":"Amnesia (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character suffers from memory loss and has difficulties remembering the past.</p>\n<p>The character is forgetful and has difficulties remembering facts and details. The character ought not to rely purely on personal memory when making decisions. They do not forget everything but apply a penalty of -3 to any roll involving recall, such as making lore or history rolls without references.</p>","flawName":"Amnesia","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Intellect"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PbLHGPIV6I00Cx91"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"xq25Jrl9hkXRligc"}
{"name":"Lack of Situational Awareness (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character often acts irately, with a distinct lack of understanding for proper behaviour and without concern for others as he or she cannot intuitively grasp behavioural patterns. Apply a -2 penalty to all social actions.</p>","flawName":"Lack of Situational Awareness","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Awareness"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"yqVR4Sw4C2FDkJwb"}
{"name":"No Sense of Smell","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>Characters with no sense of smell often have no sense of taste either and are unable to enjoy culinary delights. Characters with this affliction are especially vulnerable to spoiled food, poisonous gas and toxins because they are simply unable to detect them.</p>","flawName":"No Sense of Smell","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Awareness"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"zAdE1xIYCUyt3nbI"}
{"name":"Social Stigma (Mild)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character belongs to a faction, species or occupation, which is considered inferior or abhorrent to the general population of Llyhn. He or she is easily recognisable as belonging to this group and meets bias accordingly. Harlots, certain religious groups, slaves and the like are examples of stigmatised groups.</p>\n<p>The character belongs to a group usually looked down upon. People tend to disassociate themselves from the character, whose viewpoints are often discounted, harshly confronted or not taken seriously. The character often finds him- or herself being ignored or even excluded when in social situations, even if they express the same views as others.</p>","flawName":"Social Stigma","severity":"Mild","associatedAbility":"Presence"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pwnxlIos8y9SyM7j"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"zoKmZcV1BYT3v1j9"}
{"name":"Easily Exhausted (Moderate)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"flaw","data":{"description":"<p>The character&rsquo;s muscles tire and acidify quickly, leaving him or her are unable to maintain feats of strength for very long. Actions included are climbing, carrying heavy loads, fighting and any other tiring activities as determined by the Arbiter. The Strength score and flaw severity determine how long the character can function at normal capacity. After that, the character suffers a -1 penalty to all physical actions for each period exceeding the time limit.</p>\n<p>The character can maintain arduous manual labour for up 15 seconds (5 combat rounds).</p>","flawName":"Easily Exhausted","severity":"Moderate","associatedAbility":"Strength"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"zsgxSj0PqyS7Bx1C"}
